<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA50">
<l>cūḻnta tuḻāyalaṅkaṟ cōti maṇimuṭimā</l>
<l>ṟāḻnta varuvit taṭavaraivā – yāḻnta</l>
<l>maṇinīrc cuṉaivaḷarnta māmutalai koṉṟā</l>
<l>ṉaṇinīla vaṇṇat tavaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Māl with the flashing jewel crown with a tulsi garland all around</l>
<l>killed the big crocodile  that had grown in the pool with sapphire water</l> 
<l>on the broad mountain into which plunges the descending waterfall,</l>
<l>he with adorning blue [lotus] colour.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
